{"tid":227353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（決戰）崆峒派掌門人向MMA徐曉冬下戰書！","createTime":"2017-05-03T06:18:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T11:33:35.000Z","uid":29314,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c355bf51112b649ab4a029ec21290ccc3bc2f5c9","tid":227353,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T06:18:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/552662/xlarge/45a4c19c119d3633f5534f77de8e83ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F552662%2Fxlarge%2F45a4c19c119d3633f5534f77de8e83ae.jpg&h=9405958a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\n\r<br />\nMMA「格鬥狂人」徐曉冬27日「秒殺」「楊氏太極拳傳承人」、「雷公太極」創始人雷雷的比賽視頻持續引發網絡熱議，勝出比賽的徐曉冬這幾日繼續「串嘴」，不但批評傳統武術騙人，指中國武術的代表人物李小龍僅是「業餘高手」並非「格鬥高手」外，還宣布挑戰整個武林，同意接受其他武林掌門人的挑戰。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;經過幾日發酵後，河南焦作陳家溝多名「陳氏太極」弟子，終向徐曉冬發出戰書，希望替太極拳「討回公道」。更有傳崆峒派掌門人也向徐曉冬發出戰書，並稱規則為「無限制格鬥，死傷由命」。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/552642/xlarge/57e66d21b304f42f8837dd49f821d10d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F552642%2Fxlarge%2F57e66d21b304f42f8837dd49f821d10d.jpg&h=648d05f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b6aef18561e424cf642d87538f722f64283ef4e0","tid":227353,"uid":38653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T06:21:51.000Z","msg":"崆峒派既七傷拳<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc664b6c82eeba5ee80d8163b81dc54518b9de3c","tid":227353,"uid":6959,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T06:22:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7819f4b4271eb8ce99cce75953b794f10e148c6d","tid":227353,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T06:22:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>崆峒派既七傷拳<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n謝遜"},{"pid":"b643878f7757820ff01b938940c9baf0e5ad9fda","tid":227353,"uid":51532,"like":